## OutcomeType → Story Element Mapping

See `src/docs/.OUTCOMES.md` for the full phase-by-phase breakdown of how `OutcomeType` IDs map to
domain objects and how `TextSubmission.currentText` flows into story fields.

## Player Classes & Repercussions

See `src/docs/.CLASSES.md` for how player classes gate repercussion types, how repercussions are
attached to text additions, and how they resolve into traits, titles, and companions on players.

## Player Character Lifecycle

See `src/docs/.PLAYER_LIFECYCLE.md` for the full arc of a player character from joining and class
selection through encounter resolution, repercussion accumulation, and epilogue.

The short version: `CollaborativeTextHelper.submitTextAddition` accepts submissions, and
`calculateWinningSubmission` converts them into story elements. `getOutcomeTypes` tells each player
what they are assigned to write about for the current phase.

---

## Unimplemented / Placeholder States

| State(s) | Notes |
|---|---|
| `SET_TRAITS` / `WHO_ARE_YOU` | Guarded by `includeTraits=true`; not yet implemented |
| `WHAT_DOES_IT_MEAN` | Same guard; not yet implemented |
| `CAMPFIRE` / `CAMPFIRE_WINNERS` | Has PhaseBaseInfo for rounds 1–4 but no transition leads here |
| `NAVIGATE_VOTING` | Directional (N/S/E/W) voting — not wired into current flow |
| `EPILOGUE_PREAMBLE` / `LOCATION_SELECT_COLLABORATIVE` | Defined but not triggered |

